name: Cataclysmic Bellowing Colder
desc: If a face-up WIND monster you control is destroyed by battle or an opponent's card effect: You can Special Summon this card from your hand, then you can return 1 Spell/Trap on the field to the top of the Deck. You can only use the effect of "Cataclysmic Bellowing Colder" only once per turn.
